ZymoBIOMICS microbial community 'phyloseq' object.

ps.Rd

A 'phyloseq' class object with 195 taxa in 8 samples that are from seven rounds of six-fold dilutions (1:1 up to 1:279,936) from standard ZymoBIOMICS microbial community and 10 negative extraction controls.

ps

Format

An object of class 'phyloseq'.

SubjectID

IDs for each sample

sampleID

IDs for each sample

SampleType

A factor variable with two levels: Standard and Negative

Names

Extended names of the sampleIDs

Source

Valdiation data for the BARBI method (manuscript is under review)

Examples

if (FALSE) sample_data(ps)
otu_table(ps)
#> Error in otu_table(ps): could not find function "otu_table"
